{
  "texts": [
    "This decentralized approach ensures data privacy while leveraging the collective knowledge of the network.",
    "The cloud acts as a central entity for model aggregation, enabling efficient collaboration and real-time response in the anomaly detection process.",
    "The current anomaly detection methodologies can be improved largely in terms of accuracy, energy consumption, or scalability, thereby, the need for novel approaches is large.",
    "There is a lack of sufficient resource-aware anomaly detection techniques suitable for WSNs.",
    "Existing methods do not sufficiently address the need for accurate detection while conserving energy and minimizing communication overhead.There is a need for optimized anomaly detection in WSNs."
  ]
}